title: Cristiano Ronaldo signs with Saudi Arabian side Al-Nassr FC

title: Romanian court rules social media influencer Andrew Tate to be detained for 30 days

title: UK expected to require travellers from China to provide negative COVID test

title: 'The war changed everything': Ukraine's top performers forced to grapple war and music
description: Slogans of solidarity with Ukraine have been spray-painted on walls, hung from banners and sung on stages across the world.

title: Trump warns of 'horrible things for so many people' after his tax returns are released
description: In response to the release of thousands of pages of his tax returns, former US president Donald Trump warned "horrible things" were to come, taking aim at "radical left Democrats".

title: Former Pope Benedict XVI 'stable' and able to 'rest well' overnight, Vatican says
description: Former Pope Benedict XVI is "stable" and was able to "rest well" last night, the Vatican has said.

title: Greta Thunberg takes another swipe at Andrew Tate with pizza box jibe

title: Indian cricket star 'dozed off' before fireball car crash

title: Spain becomes second European country to announce COVID restrictions for travellers from China

title: 'To play like Pele is to play like God': What other players said of the Brazilian great

title: Ousted Myanmar leader Aung San Suu Kyi jailed for another seven years

title: Brazil begins three days of mourning after death of Pele
description: Brazil has entered three days of mourning following the death of football superstar Pele.
